### JavaScript Control Structures

```javascript
// Conditional example
if (isLoggedIn) {
    console.log('Welcome back!');
} else {
    console.log('Please log in.');
}

// Loop example
for (let i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
    console.log(i);
}
```

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Condition}
    B -->|True| C[Execute Code Block]
    B -->|False| D[Skip Code Block]
    C --> E[End]
    D --> E
```

### Control Structure Types:

| Type | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| Conditional | Execute code based on conditions |
| Loop | Repeat code execution |
